{
  "stem": "13911.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll tell you what.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My sister's father-in-law-- very distinguished old man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or maybe he wasn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe he was younger than I am now, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But, you know, when you're young, and a man with a white beard-- So even your parent-- my parents were young, but they're your parents, so they're old, you know.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know who took the first-- but my sister's father-in-law, when it came to his-- his turn to have a drink, he said, give it to the children.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and-- we-- and it was given to me and to my little friend, who was a relative of them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He-- But I'll soon-- I'll soon tell you what the consequences were, after that 15 days.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "By that was-- wasn't it, like, noble-- I just remember him saying, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Let the children have it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Like he didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And everybody got a drink of that stale, yucky water that you wouldn't even dare to drink now.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "What water meant for me, from that day on, I must say, now-- I-- I do remember, now and then, but not always.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But for so, so many years after the war, every time I would go to that sink and open up the-- and-- and get water, and I say, for goodness sake!",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "People just don't realize what they possess!",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Anytime they feel like it, they just turn the faucet and they drink water.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Water-- [SIGH] I just can't explain.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even now, it seem, was it, really?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But how do you live without-- without food and without water?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the sun is-- the sun is baking you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You're baked in the sun, and no water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All we wanted-- take us out already, but give us a drink of water.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Eventually, 15 days.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
